liri-cmake-shared
------------------------------------------
Shared CMake functions and macros for Liri

Runtime requirements:

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  cmake-3.17.3-2
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  ninja-1.10.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/lirios/cmake-shared

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/lirios/cmake-shared/archive/v1.1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack liri-cmake-shared-1.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./liri-cmake-shared-1.1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/liri-cmake-shared-1.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liri-cmake-shared-1.1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(liri-cmake-shared)
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/cmake/LiriCMakeSharedConfig.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/cmake/LiriCMakeSharedConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriAddExecutable.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriAddIndicator.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriAddModule.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriAddPlugin.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriAddQmlModule.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriAddQmlPlugin.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriAddSettingsModule.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriAddTest.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriBuild.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriCreateGitHeadRevisionFile.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriGitRevision.h.in
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriModuleConfig.cmake.in
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriModuleVersion.h.in
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriPlatformSupport.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriQDoc.cmake
  /usr/share/LiriCMakeShared/modules/LiriSetup.cmake
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/liri-cmake-shared.README
  /usr/share/doc/liri-cmake-shared/LICENSE.BSD
  /usr/share/doc/liri-cmake-shared/README.md

